{"tid":1972503,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"防彈師妹要來了！挖角「少女時代、Red Velvet推手」催生　BigHit新女團名稱曝光","createTime":"2020-04-14T14:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T23:11:09.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b856140b66ab426ad165247537f7518b18997d14","tid":1972503,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"旗下擁有天團防彈少年團（BTS）、人氣男團Tomorrow X Togerher（TXT）的南韓經紀公司Big Hit娛樂，自從2015年解散女團GLAM後，連女練習生都全數解除合約，成為KPOP出名的「和尚公司」。不過該公司在2019年宣布將重新推出女團，如今團體名稱也曝光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4677/d4677822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4677%2Fd4677822.jpg&h=d123dfb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Big Hit娛樂目前旗下都是男藝人，被戲稱是「和尚學校」。（圖／翻攝自Big Hit娛樂臉書）<br />\n<br />\nBig Hit娛樂在2019年大動作挖角前SM王牌理事閔熙珍，她在SM娛樂的9年當中，曾參與少女時代、SHINee、f(x)、EXO、Red Velvet的創立，Big Hit娛樂創辦人房時爀坦言，邀請閔熙珍加入，就是希望藉助她的經驗，打造久違的女子團體。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4677/d4677821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4677%2Fd4677821.jpg&h=5facd857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Big Hit娛樂目前旗下都是男藝人，被戲稱是「和尚學校」。（圖／翻攝自Big Hit娛樂臉書）<br />\n<br />\n14日有網友挖出Big Hit娛樂的商標註冊紀錄，發現新女團名稱就叫做「HYBE」，時間甚至是在Tomorrow X Togerher出道前就已經完成登記。此外也找出了以該名稱設置的推特和IG帳號，連LOGO都全部曝光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4816/d4816646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4816%2Fd4816646.jpg&h=f1488fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Big Hit娛樂新女團名稱曝光，已經註冊「HYBE」的商標。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n不少網友驚訝的說：「印象中才剛聽到要海選，就已經準備出道了嗎？」也有人認為，應該是先前合併的GFriend經紀公司「Source娛樂」的女練習生組成。不過也有網友表示：「TXT也是在出道前兩年就註冊了商標。」、「之前年會上有說，女團預計2021年出道。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4816/d4816647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4816%2Fd4816647.jpg&h=3de28f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Big Hit娛樂為新女團「HYBE」申請的官方社群帳號也曝光。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4816/d4816645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4816%2Fd4816645.jpg&h=7fc78854&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d4c5e1058a16c03e65919a9bc28e58ef099f197","tid":1972503,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"又多一個女團可以anti<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b640339a902f4e5d0b67458ecb8a1ca55f8ce402","tid":1972503,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d4c5e1058a16c03e65919a9bc28e58ef099f197","tid":1972503,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"又多一個女團可以anti<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"你個D圖就收返埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48313c1212016968b5a5f6b76262cc33ce40de97","tid":1972503,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b640339a902f4e5d0b67458ecb8a1ca55f8ce402","tid":1972503,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d4c5e1058a16c03e65919a9bc28e58ef099f197","tid":1972503,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"又多一個女團可以anti<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"你個D圖就收返埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:27:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"79f589048b0c14f4816baa84b038490d44f6b723","tid":1972503,"uid":132174,"like":0,"disl